Subject: [PATCH] printk: nbcon: Introduce printing kthreads

References: bsc#1214683 (PREEMPT_RT prerequisite backports)
Git-commit: 88722ff944ceff70b750e4eb753e651c2a296268
Patch-mainline: Queued in subsystem maintainer repository (v6.10-rc1-rt1)
Git-repo: git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/rt/linux-rt-devel.git

Provide the main implementation for running a printer kthread
per nbcon console that is takeover/handover aware.

Co-developed-by: John Ogness <john.ogness@linutronix.de>
